high_descs: walk forward then turn right on the sink counter
Pick up the turner on the counter
Turn left then face the sink on the right
Put the turner in the sink and rinse it
Turn right then face to the left facing the counter
Put the turner on the counter
anns.task_desc: Put the clean turner on the counter

high_descs: Walk to the spatula on the counter to your right.
Grab the spatula on the counter.
Turn left and walk to the sink to your right.
Place the spatula inside the sink, wash it and remove it.
Turn right and walk back to the counter to your left.
Place the spatula on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean spatula on the counter.

high_descs: Walk forward and turn right to face the counter
Pick up the spatula from the counter
Walk to the sink on the left
Put the spatula in the sink next to the fork, fill the sink with water, drain the sink, and take out the spatula
Put the spatula on the counter
anns.task_desc: Wash the spatula in the sink
